{
  "texts": [
    "Anyone who experiments with AI for, e.g.",
    "text summarization, develops an intuitive sense of when the AI provides the main idea sufficiently well for a given purpose and when it is worth going straight to the source.",
    "We assume that individuals cannot foresee the future, but they do observe in common the realized rewards from previous rounds.",
    "The decision also depends on each individual's type.",
    "Specifically, n individuals have types Θ n drawn from a lognormal distribution with µ = 1, σ = 0.5."
  ]
}